DJ Mixersmith is a hungarian DJ; he\&#039;s worked since 1992 in several clubs, ex. Club Speed (Hungary)or Maximal 93 (Germany), etc - all around the world. In style house, techno, trance, pumping and goa. He plays from vinyl, cd and mp3 as well - however he prefer vinyl and mixing manual. He is known by his technic: he plays more track at the same time - generating a brand new and cool sound.
